Package org.jvoicexml.event.plain

The plain package contains classes for all events that happen normally, extending PlainEvent.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CancelEvent The user has requested to cancel playing of the current prompt.
ConnectionDisconnectHangupEvent The user has hung up.
ConnectionDisconnectTransferEvent The user has been transferred unconditionally to another line and will not return.
ExitEvent The user has asked to exit.
HelpEvent The user has asked for help.
MaxspeechtimeoutEvent The user input was too long exceeding the 'maxspeechtimeout' property.
NoinputEvent The user has not responded within the timeout interval.
NomatchEvent The user input something, but it was not recognized.
 

Package org.jvoicexml.event.plain Description

The plain package contains classes for all events that happen normally, extending PlainEvent.
